Sundaram Ravi (born 22 April 1966) is a cricket umpire from India 
and a member of the ICC Elite Panel of Umpires.
He has umpired several Test matches, One Day Internationals as well as Twenty20 Internationals.
He was elevated to the Elite Panel of ICC Umpires in 2015 and became the second Indian umpire 
after Srinivasaraghavan Venkataraghavan ever to be a member of the Elite panel.
He was selected as one of the twenty umpires to stand in matches during the 2015 Cricket World Cup.